        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 21 at 6:21PM CDT until July 21 at 6:45PM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 620 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located 5 miles east of
Slapout, or 9 miles southwest of Laverne, moving northeast at 10 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible. Hail
damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Follett and Slapout.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
